      <unittitle>Max Barth Papers<unitdate normal="1916/1962" type="inclusive">1916-1962</unitdate></unittitle>
      <abstract label="Abstract:">The Correctional Association of New York Records includes records
        from the Board of Directors, annual reports, prison visit files, Narcotics Committee files,
        program and bureau files, project files, subject files, and publications. The only records
        of the organization available from the nineteenth century are the annual reports, which have
        been microfilmed and are available in the University Library.</abstract>
