    <bioghist>
      <head>Biographical History</head>
      <p>Max Barth was born in Waldkirch in Baden-Wurttemberg, Germany.He was a poet, writer,  and journalist.  Barth founded his own small weekly newspaper, <emph render="italic">The Direction</emph>. </p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>Photocopies of handcorrected typescripts of poetry, 19161940; and offprints of articles, 19611962. </p>
    </scopecontent>
    <arrangement>
      <head>Arrangement of the Collection</head>
